data.description: REDUCED over $75k !.This property is located in the Tranquil and Friendly Oak Trace Community. Step into this beautifully remodeled 2348 sq. ft. home that is nestled on a quiet cul-de-sac with well over $80,000 in upgrade done in 2023. This home features four bedrooms, two baths, and your very own private in-ground pool in a screened in lanai. Upon entering the double doors, you'll find a spacious living room and a formal dining room perfect for entertaining and creating cherished memories. The primary bedroom offers two walk-in closets and an ensuite bathroom with a separate bath, walk-in shower, and double sinks. Two of the additional bedrooms also feature walk-in closets, and there's a linen closet in the hallway for extra storage.The kitchen boasts wood cabinets and comes equipped with stainless steel appliances. The laundry room includes a washer, dryer, and a built-in utility sink.The interior has been freshly painted including the elevated ceilings and boasts all-new 5 3/4 inch baseboards.The remodel includes a brand new 30-YEAR ROOF with Warranty, gutter downspouts, an Energy-Efficient Pool Pump System, a NEW 55-gallon Rheem HOT WATER HEATER, and a cutting-edge CARRIER INFINITY 5 TIER variable-speed AC UNIT.  You'll find NEW Water-Resistant Flooring thru-out, new lighting, smoke detectors, kitchen and bathroom granite countertops, new sinks and faucets, garbage disposal, three hurricane impact windows. One photo virtually staged. Make an appointment today and start living your best life.
